text: Víctor Crisólogo (1952 – 17 January 2021) was a Peruvian politician. He was a member of the Congress of the Republic of Peru from 2011 to 2016. He was a member of the Possible Peru. He was born in Virú, Peru. Crisólogo died on 17 January 2021 in the Nuevo Chimbote District, Peru from COVID-19, aged 68. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Peruvian politicians Category:Deaths from the COVID-19 pandemic in Peru Category:People from Chimbote
